cl_sql = """
WITH PORT_CODE AS (
	SELECT DISTINCT 
		CHEONG_CODE
		,PORT
	FROM 20001_DB.TERMINAL_INFO_TBL tit 
),
DDTV2 AS (
	SELECT DISTINCT PORT_CODE.PORT, ddtv.CALLSIGN, ddtv.ATA, ddtv.ATD
	FROM PORT_CODE
	JOIN 20001_DB.DEOCOS_DEOVAD_TBL_V3 ddtv 
	ON ddtv.PRTC = PORT_CODE.CHEONG_CODE
)
SELECT vtwclav.*, DDTV2.ATA, DDTV2.ATD
FROM 20001_DB.VESSEL_TERMINAL_WHARF_CNTR_LOAD_AMOUNT_V2 vtwclav 
JOIN DDTV2
ON vtwclav.PORT_CODE = DDTV2.PORT
AND vtwclav.CALLSIGN =  DDTV2.CALLSIGN
WHERE vtwclav.IN_OUT_TIME_DT BETWEEN DDTV2.ATA AND DDTV2.ATD
"""

  • I_CNT와 E_CNT가 둘 다 발생한 경우만 센 것

    WITH PORT_CODE AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT

     CHEONG_CODE  
 ,PORT

    FROM 20001_DB.TERMINAL_INFO_TBL tit
    ),
    DDTV2 AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT PORT_CODE.PORT, ddtv.CALLSIGN, ddtv.ATA, ddtv.ATD
    FROM PORT_CODE
    JOIN 20001_DB.DEOCOS_DEOVAD_TBL_V3 ddtv
    ON ddtv.PRTC = PORT_CODE.CHEONG_CODE
    ),
    DDTV_TP AS (
    SELECT vtwclav.*, DDTV2.ATA, DDTV2.ATD
    FROM 20001_DB.VESSEL_TERMINAL_WHARF_CNTR_LOAD_AMOUNT_V2 vtwclav
    JOIN DDTV2
    ON vtwclav.PORT_CODE = DDTV2.PORT
    AND vtwclav.CALLSIGN = DDTV2.CALLSIGN
    WHERE vtwclav.IN_OUT_TIME_DT BETWEEN DDTV2.ATA AND DDTV2.ATD
    )
    SELECT TERMINAL, PORT_CODE, BERTH, CALLSIGN, ATA, ATD
    ,SUM(CASE WHEN IE_TYPE = 'I' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS I_CNT
    ,SUM(CASE WHEN IE_TYPE = 'E' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS E_CNT
    FROM DDTV_TP
    GROUP BY TERMINAL, PORT_CODE, BERTH, CALLSIGN, ATA, ATD
    HAVING I_CNT > 1 AND E_CNT >1

Dual Cycling 작업 수 세기¶

In [ ]:
df_dual_cycling_group['E_count'] = 0 
df_dual_cycling_group['I_count'] = 0 
df_dual_cycling_group['Dual_E_count'] = 0 ## ('IE_TYPE'='E')  min_I <= IN_OUT_TIME <= max_I
df_dual_cycling_group['Dual_I_count'] = 0
df_dual_cycling_group['Dual_E_percent'] = 0.
df_dual_cycling_group['Dual_I_percent'] = 0.

df_dual_berth_is_nan_idx = np.where(df_dual_cycling_group['BERTH'].isna())[0]

for j in range(len(df_dual_cycling_group)):
    if j%100==0:
        print(j)
    temp_dual = df_dual_cycling_group.iloc[j,:-8].values
    
    if j in list(df_dual_berth_is_nan_idx):
        temp_fn_indexing = temp_fn.loc[np.where((temp_fn['TERMINAL']==temp_dual[0]) & (temp_fn['PORT_CODE']==temp_dual[1]) & (temp_fn['BERTH'].isna()) & (temp_fn['CALLSIGN']==temp_dual[3]) & (temp_fn['ATA']==temp_dual[4]) & (temp_fn['ATD']==temp_dual[5]))[0],:]
    else:
        temp_fn_indexing = temp_fn.loc[np.where((temp_fn['TERMINAL']==temp_dual[0]) & (temp_fn['PORT_CODE']==temp_dual[1]) & (temp_fn['BERTH']==temp_dual[2]) & (temp_fn['CALLSIGN']==temp_dual[3]) & (temp_fn['ATA']==temp_dual[4]) & (temp_fn['ATD']==temp_dual[5]))[0],:]
    temp_fn_indexing = temp_fn_indexing.reset_index()
    
    e_minTime = df_dual_cycling_group.loc[j, 'E_minTime']
    e_maxTime = df_dual_cycling_group.loc[j, 'E_maxTime']
    i_minTime = df_dual_cycling_group.loc[j, 'I_minTime']
    i_maxTime = df_dual_cycling_group.loc[j, 'I_maxTime']
    
    e_cnt, i_cnt, dual_e_cnt, dual_i_cnt = 0,0,0,0
    for r in temp_fn_indexing.loc[:,['IE_TYPE', 'IN_OUT_TIME_DT2']].values:
        if r[0] == 'I':
            i_cnt+=1
            if e_minTime <= r[1] <= e_maxTime:
                dual_i_cnt+= 1
        else:
            e_cnt+=1
            if i_minTime <= r[1] <= i_maxTime:
                dual_e_cnt+= 1
                
    df_dual_cycling_group.loc[j,'Dual_E_count'] = dual_e_cnt
    df_dual_cycling_group.loc[j,'Dual_I_count'] = dual_i_cnt
    df_dual_cycling_group.loc[j,'E_count'] = e_cnt
    df_dual_cycling_group.loc[j,'I_count'] = i_cnt
      
## 각 작업별, Dual_E_percent :: E 작업 중 Dual작업의 비율 
## 각 작업별, Dual_I_percent :: I 작업 중 Dual작업의 비율 
df_dual_cycling_group['Dual_E_percent'] = (df_dual_cycling_group['Dual_E_count'] / df_dual_cycling_group['E_count'])*100
df_dual_cycling_group['Dual_I_percent'] = (df_dual_cycling_group['Dual_I_count'] / df_dual_cycling_group['I_count'])*100

df_dual_cycling_group.to_csv('../test_data/df_dual_cycling_group.csv',index=None)

def indexing_df_by_join_cond(j):
    temp_dual = df_dual_cycling_group.iloc[j,:-8].values

    if j in list(df_dual_berth_is_nan_idx):
        temp_fn_indexing = temp_fn.loc[np.where((temp_fn['TERMINAL']==temp_dual[0]) & (temp_fn['PORT_CODE']==temp_dual[1]) & (temp_fn['BERTH'].isna()) & (temp_fn['CALLSIGN']==temp_dual[3]) & (temp_fn['ATA']==temp_dual[4]) & (temp_fn['ATD']==temp_dual[5]))[0],:]
    else:
        temp_fn_indexing = temp_fn.loc[np.where((temp_fn['TERMINAL']==temp_dual[0]) & (temp_fn['PORT_CODE']==temp_dual[1]) & (temp_fn['BERTH']==temp_dual[2]) & (temp_fn['CALLSIGN']==temp_dual[3]) & (temp_fn['ATA']==temp_dual[4]) & (temp_fn['ATD']==temp_dual[5]))[0],:]
    temp_fn_indexing = temp_fn_indexing.reset_index()
    return temp_fn_indexing
